{
    "json_version": 0x2,
    "name": "EVENT_MESSAGE_MM04_ST3_070.ebm",
    "nb_messages": 0x17,
    "messages": [
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xa,
            "name_id": 0xa,
            "extra_id": 0x2d,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x0,
            "msg_string": "Oh, hi, Ayesha. Have you heard the recent ghost rumors?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x122,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "What!? Gh-Gh-Ghost?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xa,
            "name_id": 0xa,
            "extra_id": 0x1a8,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "Yup. From what I've heard, she appears all over this hill."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x126,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x3,
            "msg_string": "Hyaaah...! M-Maybe somebody just mistook something for a ghost..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xa,
            "name_id": 0xa,
            "extra_id": 0x2e,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x4,
            "msg_string": "On his way home from work, late one night, someone saw a girl."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xa,
            "name_id": 0xa,
            "extra_id": 0x2e,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x5,
            "msg_string": "I guess he went to warn her that it's not safe to wander around at night all by herself..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xa,
            "name_id": 0xa,
            "extra_id": 0x2f,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x6,
            "msg_string": "But the girl totally ignored him and just kept looking the other way."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xa,
            "name_id": 0xa,
            "extra_id": 0x76,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x7,
            "msg_string": "At first, he just thought she was being rude, so he tried to get her attention again. But then..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xa,
            "name_id": 0xa,
            "extra_id": 0x78,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x8,
            "msg_string": "He realized that the girl was standing above the hill, in mid-air..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x127,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x9,
            "msg_string": "Hyaaah! So, she was just floating there...!?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xa,
            "name_id": 0xa,
            "extra_id": 0x1a6,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xa,
            "msg_string": "Yup. When he took a closer look, he noticed she looked kind of blurry, and seemed to be bathed in a gloomy light."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xa,
            "name_id": 0xa,
            "extra_id": 0x27,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xb,
            "msg_string": "And then, the girl muttered something about medicinal herbs and candy, or something..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x128,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xc,
            "msg_string": "Th-This is too scary!<CR>...Wait, medicinal herbs and candy?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xa,
            "name_id": 0xa,
            "extra_id": 0x2e,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xd,
            "msg_string": "The guy got so scared, he ran right home, but..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xa,
            "name_id": 0xa,
            "extra_id": 0x2f,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xe,
            "msg_string": "Since then, eyewitness reports have<CR>been flooding in. I heard she even<CR>appeared...right in front of this shop."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xa,
            "name_id": 0xa,
            "extra_id": 0xf5,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0xf,
            "msg_string": "People have heard the ghost murmuring \"Sis,\" too... How scary is that!?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x10,
            "msg_string": "...Sis? Could it be...?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xa,
            "name_id": 0xa,
            "extra_id": 0xf7,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x11,
            "msg_string": "Ayesha, you better be careful.<CR>After all, you do live alone."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x193,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x12,
            "msg_string": "Oh, okay... But that girl...may not be a ghost..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xa,
            "name_id": 0xa,
            "extra_id": 0x15a,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x13,
            "msg_string": "Huh? How would you know? Do you know her or something?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x14,
            "msg_string": "Know her and more... Ah, hahaha..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x15,
            "msg_string": "(Nio, other people are starting to see you...)"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x16,
            "msg_string": "(I'm sure you don't mean to, but you shouldn't scare people like that...)"
        }
    ]
}